V0513_01_00_00_0.text: Welcome to my wonderful world of Dueltaining!

V0513_01_00_02_0.text: A Dueltainer never turns down a Duel!

V0513_01_00_03_0.text: Prepare for a performance you've never seen before!

V0513_01_00_03_1.text: A Dueltaining display of dynamic dimensions!

V0513_01_00_04_0.text: I love to have fun, but I also love to win!

V0513_01_00_05_0.text: Let's make this a Duel we can both enjoy!

V0513_01_00_06_0.text: Before this Duel is over, the crowd'll be chanting my name!

V0513_01_00_07_0.text: No one can thrill a throng like two daring Dueltainers!

V0513_01_00_08_0.text: Can't wait to see what You Show Duel School taught you!

V0513_01_00_09_0.text:
You're finally here, Yuri.
Let's begin!

V0513_03_00_00_0.text: Are you ready for the main event!

V0513_03_00_01_0.text: This Duel can use a dash of more derring-do!

V0513_03_00_04_0.text:
Don't worry!
I still have plenty of show left!

V0513_03_00_05_0.text: The threat of danger and defeat is what creates the drama!

V0513_05_00_00_0.text: If you paid for a ticket, you deserve to see a show!

V0513_06_01_01_0.text:
I knew you'd try that.
However!

V0513_07_09_00_0.text: I flip over my Set card!

V0513_07_09_01_0.text: Check out the card I Set!

V0513_10_00_02_0.text: Turn your eyes to the stage!

V0513_11_01_00_0.text: I Summon a monster in Defense Position!

V0513_11_08_01_0.text:
I'll build the Overlay Network!
Xyz Summon!

V0513_11_09_01_1.text: It's time for my monsters to shine in the spotlight!

V0513_16_00_00_0.text: This grand finale is gonna be fabulous!

V0513_16_00_01_0.text: I'll end this Duel in style!

V0513_21_00_00_0.text: Much more exciting than you expected, huh?

V0513_21_00_01_0.text: Let's see if you can leap to my level.

V0513_21_00_02_0.text: With that, I end my turn!

V0513_21_00_03_1.text:
It's your turn!
Make sure you hype up the crowd!

V0513_21_00_04_0.text: I need to work harder to wow the crowd!

V0513_21_00_05_0.text:
Give up? Why?
I have so many more secrets in store!

V0513_28_00_00_0.text: This Duel was a lot of fun for me too!

V0513_28_00_01_0.text: Now that we've Dueled, I consider you my friend!

V0513_28_00_02_0.text: You need a lot more training to be a Dueltainer like moi!

V0513_28_00_03_0.text:
Hmm...
This Duel was okay - but not the best.

V0513_28_00_03_1.text: You need to come up with a bunch more surprises!

V0513_28_00_04_0.text: Nothing's greater than capturing the hearts of the crowd!

V0513_28_00_05_0.text: Sorry I had to snatch your victory.

V0513_28_00_06_0.text: Once you polish your skills to a shine, let's Duel again!

V0513_28_00_07_0.text:
You think I cheated?
I'll take that as a compliment!

V0513_28_00_08_0.text: If I can make people smile again, maybe they'll forgive me.

V0513_29_00_00_0.text:
Hey!
You're quite the star yourself!

V0513_29_00_02_0.text: The crowd loves a winner - so these cheers are for you!

V0513_29_00_04_0.text: A big round of applause for today's victor!

V0513_29_00_05_0.text: Did you learn those tricks by Dueltaining your dad?

V0513_29_00_06_0.text: You Show Duel School taught you well!

V0513_29_00_07_0.text:
Sigh...
I can never outduel you, Yuri.

V0513_33_00_01_0.text: Get ready for an illusion you've never seen before!

V0513_33_00_02_0.text: If I pull off this trick, I expect a nice round of applause!

V0513_34_00_00_0.text: I didn't like what you did last turn.

V0513_34_00_01_0.text:
Ready to witness a miracle?
One... two... three!

V0513_34_00_02_0.text: Is that supposed to be funny?

V0513_34_00_03_0.text: I'll pretend I didn't see that♪

V0513_34_00_05_0.text:
You have a Rank-Up-Magic in your hand!
How do I know? Magic!

V0513_34_00_06_0.text: A magician never reveals his tricks!

V0513_34_00_09_0.text: Is this the card you wanted to see?

V0513_34_00_10_0.text: I should take this Duel a tad more seriously.

V0513_34_00_11_0.text: Now that you know who I really am, prepare to be hunted!

V0513_34_00_12_0.text:
Argh!
Luck's just not on my side...

V0513_35_00_01_0.text: Let's give these Duel Links fans the greatest show ever!

V0513_36_00_00_0.text:
I've done my part.
You handle the grand finale!

V0513_36_00_02_0.text:
Don't worry!
You still have me and my Trapeze Magician!

V0513_36_00_03_0.text:
You're up, Yuya!
Dueltain your way to a win!

V0513_36_00_05_0.text:
It'll be fine, Yuya!
Just relax!

V0513_36_00_06_0.text: It's all up to you, Yuri.

V0513_36_00_08_0.text: This should be easy for you, Yuri.

V0513_08_00_00_0.text: Nothing says fun and excitement like getting bubbly!

V0513_08_00_00_1.text: I activate the Continuous Spell, Bubble Barrier!

V0513_08_00_01_0.text:
I’ve got a cool trick to show you!
One... two... three!

V0513_08_00_01_1.text: I activate the Trap Card, Trick Box!

V0513_08_00_03_0.text: Bound Wand activates when it's sent to the Graveyard!

V0513_08_00_04_0.text:
Let's see you juggle this!
The Equip Spell, One-Shot Wand!

V0513_08_00_06_0.text:
Ready for a world of wonders?
The Equip Spell, Wonder Wand!

V0513_08_00_07_0.text:
It's showtime!
I activate Wonder Wand's effect!

V0513_08_00_08_0.text: This one card will let me eat for a week!

V0513_08_00_08_1.text: The Spell Card, Magical Stone Excavation!

V0513_08_00_09_0.text: This card's powerful in the right hands - like mine!

V0513_08_00_10_0.text: Is this what you came here to see?

V0513_08_00_11_0.text: I activate the Spell Card, Polymerization!

V0513_08_00_12_0.text:
I activate my Spell Card!
Ancient Gear Catapult!

V0513_08_00_13_0.text: I activate Ancient Gear Catapult's effect from my Graveyard!

V0513_08_00_14_0.text:
I activate my Spell Card!
Ancient Gear Workshop!

V0513_08_00_15_0.text:
I activate my Spell Card!
Ancient Gear Drill!

V0513_08_00_16_0.text: I activate my Spell Card, Ancient Gear Factory!

V0513_08_00_17_0.text: I activate the Spell Card, Ancient Gear Fusion!

V0513_08_00_18_0.text:
I activate my Spell Card!
Ancient Gear Explosive!

V0513_08_00_19_0.text:
I activate my Continuous Spell!
Ancient Gear Advance!

V0513_08_00_20_0.text: I activate Ancient Gear Advance's effect!

V0513_08_00_21_0.text:
I activate my Continuous Spell!
Ancient Gear Castle!

V0513_08_00_22_0.text: I activate the Continuous Spell, Ancient Gear Fortress!

V0513_08_00_23_0.text: If Ancient Gear Fortress is destroyed, I can use its effect!

V0513_08_00_24_0.text:
I activate my Equip Spell!
Ancient Gear Tank!

V0513_08_00_25_0.text: Ancient Gear Tank's effect activates when it's destroyed!

V0513_08_00_26_0.text: I activate the Equip Spell, Ancient Gear Fist!

V0513_08_00_28_0.text:
I activate my Continuous Trap!
Ancient Gear Reborn!

V0513_08_00_30_0.text: I activate the Field Spell, Geartown!

V0513_08_00_31_0.text: When Geartown is destroyed, its effect activates!

V0513_08_00_32_0.text:
I activate my Spell Card!
Spell Gear!

V0513_08_00_33_0.text: I activate Performage Mirror Conductor's Pendulum Effect!

V0513_09_00_00_0.text: I use 1 Overlay Unit to activate Trapeze Magician's effect!

V0513_09_00_01_0.text: Trapeze Magician uses 1 Overlay Unit to activate its effect!

V0513_09_00_01_1.text: Enjoy a show that's twice as nice!

V0513_09_00_02_0.text: Trapeze Magician's effect activates when it's destroyed!

V0513_09_00_03_0.text: I banish Stilts Launcher from the Graveyard!

V0513_09_00_04_0.text: I activate Performage Damage Juggler's effect from my hand!

V0513_09_00_05_0.text: I banish Damage Juggler from my Graveyard to use its effect!

V0513_09_00_06_0.text: Trick Clown activates when it's sent to the Graveyard!

V0513_09_00_08_0.text: I activate Performage Flame Eater's effect from my hand!

V0513_09_00_09_0.text: Flame Eater's effect activates when it's Summoned!

V0513_09_00_10_0.text: Performage Mirror Conductor activates its effect!

V0513_09_00_11_0.text: Plushfire's effect activates when it's destroyed!

V0513_09_00_12_0.text: Ultimate Ancient Gear Golem activates when it's destroyed!

V0513_09_00_13_0.text: I activate Ancient Gear Megaton Golem's effect!

V0513_09_00_14_0.text: Ancient Gear Howitzer activates its effect!

V0513_09_00_15_0.text: Howitzer's effect activates when it's destroyed in battle!

V0513_09_00_16_0.text: Ancient Gear Reactor Dragon's effect activates!

V0513_09_00_17_0.text: Ancient Gear Dark Golem's effect activates!

V0513_09_00_18_0.text: I activate Ancient Gear Golem - Ultimate Pound's effect!

V0513_09_00_19_0.text: Ultimate Pound's effect activates when it's destroyed!

V0513_09_00_20_0.text: Ancient Gear Gadjiltron Dragon's effect activates!

V0513_09_00_22_0.text: Ancient Gear Gadjiltron Chimera's effect activates!

V0513_09_00_25_0.text: Ancient Gear Box activates its effect!

V0513_09_00_26_0.text: I activate Ancient Gear Frame's effect!

V0513_09_00_27_0.text: Ancient Gear Tanker activates its effect!

V0513_09_00_28_0.text: I activate Ancient Gear Commander's effect!

V0513_09_00_29_0.text: I banish Ancient Gear Commander from my Graveyard!

V0513_09_00_30_0.text: I activate Ancient Gear Gadget's effect!

V0513_09_00_31_0.text: Hunting Hound's effect activates when it's Summoned!

V0513_09_00_32_0.text: My Hunting Hound's effect allows me to Fusion Summon!

V0513_09_00_33_0.text: I activate Ancient Gear Cannon's effect!

V0513_09_00_34_0.text: Ballista's effect activates when it's Link Summoned!

V0513_09_00_35_0.text: Ancient Gear Ballista activates its effect!

V0513_09_00_36_0.text:
Bloom Diva!
Belt out a melody!

V0513_37_00_00_0.text: Direct your gaze to the skies above!

V0513_37_00_00_1.text:
I present to you a swinging star performer!
Xyz Summon!

V0513_37_00_01_1.text: Direct your gaze to the skies above!

V0513_37_00_01_2.text:
I present to you a swinging star performer!
Xyz Summon!

V0513_13_00_07_0.text: The Pendulum Monster, Performage Mirror Conductor!

V0513_37_00_02_0.text: My kennel's ready to do my bidding!

V0513_37_00_02_1.text: Join together into an Ancient Gear of goliath proportions!

V0513_13_00_09_0.text: The ground shaking Chaos Ancient Gear Giant!

V0513_37_00_03_0.text: I unite the savagery of past ages into a brutal behemoth!

V0513_13_00_11_0.text: Here's Level 9 Ancient Gear Megaton Golem!

V0513_37_00_04_0.text: Utilize your combat experience and tactical intellect!

V0513_37_00_04_1.text: Reconfigure into a devastating war machine!

V0513_13_00_35_0.text: I Special Summon an Ancient Gear Token!

V0513_19_00_01_0.text: Watch it soar through the stratosphere towards you!

V0513_19_00_01_1.text: Take a swing at 'em, Trapeze Magician!

V0513_19_00_06_0.text:
Performage Flame Eater!
Let 'em feel the heat!

V0513_19_00_16_0.text:
Ancient Gear Golem - Ultimate Pound!
Attack!

V0513_19_00_30_0.text: Track 'em down, Ancient Gear Hunting Hound!

V0513_19_00_34_0.text:
Bloom Diva the Melodious Choir!
Attack!

V0513_44_00_02_0.text: Only one will rule the Duel...

V0513_44_00_03_0.text: In the ultimate fusion of monsters and mayhem!

V0513_27_00_01_0.text: Is this as bad as I think?
